          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618227799566-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618227799566-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped veg </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to a large bowl with a large drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>seasoned</strong> <strong>veg </strong>to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1618227804380-x200.jpg",
