        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> couscous</strong> to the bowl, then cover and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 4,
