      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to a pot over a medium-high heat</p><p>Bring to the boil, then reduce the heat to very low and cook for approx. 2-3 min or until it turns into a runny glaze that coats the back of a spoon</p><p>Tip: Watch the pan like a hawk to make sure the glaze doesn't burn!</p><p>Once done, remove the pot from the heat and set aside until serving – this is your <strong>balsamic glaze</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
