        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the<strong> cooked couscous</strong> with a fork</p><p>Carefully remove the skin from the <strong>roasted onions</strong> by cutting the root end off and peeling off the skin, then separate the onion into petals</p><p>Chop the <strong>roasted pepper</strong> into small pieces</p>",
