      "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Mix the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>veg</strong> and<strong> chopped basil</strong> through the couscous – this is your<strong> roasted</strong> <strong>veg couscous</strong></p><p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p>",
